node.text: GUY’S !! LISTEN UP. Me and my angel girlfriends @laisribeiro , @sarasampaio & @jastookes have accepted the #ALLINCHALLENGE. We have created the most incredible day for you. So if YOU WANNA WIN A FULL DAY HANGING OUT WITH THE ANGELS AND TRY WHAT ITS LIKE TO BE US : Go to the link in bio and watch this video to see what we’re offering up. Let’s all make a positive impact during this very difficult time. We wanna challenge @zedd, @zendaya, and @zacefron to go ALL IN! Donations benefit @nokidhungry, @mealsonwheelsamerica and #americasfoodfund which benefits @feedingamerica and @wckitchen LINK IN BIO

node.text: In these challenging times, let's reevaluate what's truly important and how we can all join together to help others. We're #ApartYetConnected, and I know we'll emerge from this situation even stronger as a globe. I teamed up with @vogue and some friends @thesocietynyc @therealronaldepps @young_emperors @taookamoto  @alealimay @averyginsberg @carolinetrentini @chico_lachowski  @adutakech @rawdis to share my thoughts through this united message. Stay safe everyone!
